lished correlations between outflow\nmomentum deposition rates and \"source\" luminosities, and for using these\nderived properties to estimate the ratio of mass ejection rates to mass\naccretion rates onto protostars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jun 2003 16:51:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Jul 2003 18:44:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
