ibutions of the rotational velocity of the gaseous\ncomponent and of the stellar velocity dispersion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jun 2003 12:27:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Jun 2003 14:11:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Jun 2003 07:15:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
